item.title: Kairos Club App
item.description: The App is a great tool for the clients of Kairos Club to get specific and accurate analytics about their sales, best products, informations about the current state of their inventory and Customers listing. The App generates also financial statements every month. Presentation of the different sections of the app : Statistics has 14 different types of charts which includes Maps, Timeseries and DoghnutCharts… Inventory displays a listing of all the digital and physical products of the supplier with the current state of inventory in each warehouse and the gross income.
